{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-hackers-js","path":"/hackers/manage-notifications.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"program-notifications\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#program-notifications\" aria-label=\"program notifications permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Program Notifications</h3>\n<p>As a hacker, you’ll receive notifications (via the product and email) when programs you’re subscribed to make updates. Notifications in the product will appear in the notifications box next to your profile icon.</p>\n<p>You can subscribe to receive program update notifications by subscribing to receive notifications via a program's Security Page by clicking <strong>Subscribe</strong>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 20%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"subscribe button on policy page\"\n        title=\"subscribe button on policy page\"\n        src=\"/static/847b8cac8536c27778a8bf4f194dff05/0b533/subscribe_button.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/847b8cac8536c27778a8bf4f194dff05/fac75/subscribe_button.png 125w,\n/static/847b8cac8536c27778a8bf4f194dff05/63868/subscribe_button.png 250w,\n/static/847b8cac8536c27778a8bf4f194dff05/0b533/subscribe_button.png 500w,\n/static/847b8cac8536c27778a8bf4f194dff05/1d69c/subscribe_button.png 750w,\n/static/847b8cac8536c27778a8bf4f194dff05/00d43/subscribe_button.png 1000w,\n/static/847b8cac8536c27778a8bf4f194dff05/a3c4c/subscribe_button.png 2196w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Updates to these program settings will trigger notifications:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Policy</li>\n<li>Bounty table</li>\n<li>Scope</li>\n<li>Hacker messages</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"manage-notifications\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#manage-notifications\" aria-label=\"manage notifications permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Manage Notifications</h3>\n<h4 id=\"notification-preferences\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#notification-preferences\" aria-label=\"notification preferences permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Notification Preferences</h4>\n<p>You can manage your notification preferences on the Notification Preferences page under <strong>Settings > Notification Preferences</strong>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 93.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"notification preferences\"\n        title=\"notification preferences\"\n        src=\"/static/5ddbc7883145a27b21373e01ed2e38d7/0b533/notification-preferences-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5ddbc7883145a27b21373e01ed2e38d7/fac75/notification-preferences-2.png 125w,\n/static/5ddbc7883145a27b21373e01ed2e38d7/63868/notification-preferences-2.png 250w,\n/static/5ddbc7883145a27b21373e01ed2e38d7/0b533/notification-preferences-2.png 500w,\n/static/5ddbc7883145a27b21373e01ed2e38d7/1d69c/notification-preferences-2.png 750w,\n/static/5ddbc7883145a27b21373e01ed2e38d7/00d43/notification-preferences-2.png 1000w,\n/static/5ddbc7883145a27b21373e01ed2e38d7/0d390/notification-preferences-2.png 1472w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Notifications","id":"hackers/manage-notifications","path":"/hackers/manage-notifications.html","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"Program Notifications"},{"value":"Manage Notifications"}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}